      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJESTIC LORD (8) followed a solid second on debut two runs back with a distant fourth when he broke in a 1690m event at this track. Shouldn't spend a penny from this draw and the sprint lane may come in handy. Must improve his manners but a return to form is on the cards. ZIPPIN PAST (3) finished fourth last start over 1690m at this track, beaten 9 metres, after a good win at this track the run prior. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Meets a comparable field and she is capable of a return to the winner's list. REGAL GALA (7) is in line for another win at his third career run after scoring over 1690m at this track a week-and-a-half ago. Stick with him. TRUE APLOMB (2) is at the track for the first time. By Tactical Landing and hails from the S B Cleave stable. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Looks to have some ability based on a recent trial win. Will be ready to run a big race.",
